# Julius core (voice + platform)

## Subsystems
- **Voice:** `ConversationStore` + `AgentType` + `ConversationalAgent` — not the coding harness.
- **Harness:** `CodingAgentQueueEngine`, `CodingAgentBackend`, `HarnessRoute` — see `julius-harness.mdc`.

## Key paths
- `shared/.../shared/conversation/ConversationStore.kt` — orchestration
- `shared/.../shared/voice/VoiceManager.kt` — voice interface
- `androidApp/.../AndroidVoiceManager.kt` — Android STT/TTS
- `androidApp/.../SettingsManager.kt` — `AgentType`, settings
- `androidApp/.../di/AppModule.kt` — `DynamicAgentWrapper`, Koin
- `shared/.../agents/` — agent implementations
- `androidApp/.../auto/` — Car App Library screens + `VoiceAppService`

## Patterns
- Agent switch: `SettingsManager.settings.selectedAgent` → `DynamicAgentWrapper` (no Koin reload).
- Audio: `AgentResponse.audio` → `playAudio()`; else `speak()` (system TTS).
- Keys: `local.properties`/env → `BuildConfig`; runtime Settings override.

## Build
- minSdk 26, compile/target 36, app id `fr.geoking.julius`
- Versions: `gradle/libs.versions.toml`
- Verify: `./gradlew :androidApp:compileFullDebugKotlin` before finishing tasks

## Android Auto
- No click listeners on `Pane` rows; use `ListTemplate` or actions.
- Car mic + Vosk: assets under `androidApp/src/main/assets/models/vosk/`

